    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "Khi d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en nghe tin Gi\xEA-r\xF4-b\xF4-am \u0111\xE3 tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 th\xEC h\u1ECD m\u1EDDi \xF4ng \u0111\u1EBFn d\u1EF1 m\u1ED9t bu\u1ED5i h\u1ECDp v\xE0 c\u1EED \xF4ng l\xE0m vua tr\xEAn \xCDt-ra-en. Ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 m\u1ED9t m\xECnh chi t\u1ED9c Giu-\u0111a l\xE0 c\xF2n theo nh\xE0 \u0110a-v\xEDt m\xE0 th\xF4i. "), mdx("h6", {
