  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu d\xE2n ch\xFAng ti\u1EBFp t\u1EE5c \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem \u0111\u1EC3 d\xE2ng sinh t\u1EBF th\xEC h\u1ECD r\u1EA5t c\xF3 th\u1EC3 mu\u1ED1n R\xF4-b\xF4-am cai tr\u1ECB m\xECnh. H\u1ECD s\u1EBD gi\u1EBFt ta r\u1ED3i theo R\xF4-b\xF4-am, vua Giu-\u0111a.\" "), mdx("h6", {
