    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110i\u1EC1u n\u1EA7y tr\u1EDF n\xEAn t\u1ED9i l\u1ED7i l\u1EDBn v\xEC d\xE2n ch\xFAng \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn \u0110an v\xE0 B\xEA-t\xEAn \u0111\u1EC3 th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y con b\xF2 v\xE0ng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v31"
  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "Gi\xEA-r\xF4-b\xF4-am x\xE2y c\xE1c \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD t\u1EA1i nh\u1EEFng n\u01A1i th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y. \xD4ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ECDn nh\u1EEFng th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 t\u1EEB trong d\xE2n ch\xFAng ch\u1EDB kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i trong chi t\u1ED9c L\xEA-vi m\xE0 th\xF4i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i vua \u0111\u1EB7t ra m\u1ED9t l\u1EC5 m\u1EDBi v\xE0o ng\xE0y m\u01B0\u1EDDi l\u0103m th\xE1ng t\xE1m, gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 l\u1EC5 c\u1EE7a d\xE2n Giu-\u0111a. Trong khi \u0111\xF3 vua d\xE2ng sinh t\u1EBF tr\xEAn b\xE0n th\u1EDD c\xF9ng v\u1EDBi sinh t\u1EBF d\xE2ng cho c\xE1c b\xF2 con v\xE0ng \u1EDF B\xEA-t\xEAn m\xE0 vua \u0111\xE3 d\u1EF1ng n\xEAn. Vua c\u0169ng ch\u1ECDn c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 \u1EDF B\xEA-t\xEAn \u0111\u1EC3 ph\u1EE5c v\u1EE5 c\xE1c n\u01A1i th\u1EDD ph\u1EE5ng m\xE0 vua \u0111\xE3 l\u1EADp. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v33"
  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy Gi\xEA-r\xF4-b\xF4-am t\u1EF1 ch\u1ECDn th\u1EDDi gian t\u1ED5 ch\u1EE9c l\u1EC5 cho d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en ng\xE0y m\u01B0\u1EDDi l\u0103m th\xE1ng t\xE1m. Trong th\u1EDDi gian \u0111\xF3 vua d\xE2ng sinh t\u1EBF tr\xEAn b\xE0n th\u1EDD m\xECnh \u0111\xE3 x\xE2y t\u1EA1i B\xEA-t\xEAn. Vua \u0111\u1EB7t ra l\u1EC5 cho d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 d\xE2ng sinh t\u1EBF tr\xEAn b\xE0n th\u1EDD."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
